Package de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger.debugData

Record Class GroupDebugData

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger.debugData.GroupDebugData
Record Components:
supervisor - the name of the supervisor of the group
map - a two dimensional array of type CellType which define the current map
mapTopLeft - the position of the top left Point in the map in the coordinate system of the agents
interestingPoints - a list of interesting points which are used for path finding
pathFindingResult - an two dimensional array which stores the path finding results of every agent in the group
agentPosition - the position of every agent
roleZones - all discovered role zones by the group
goalZones - all discovered goal zones by the group
agents - a list of all agent names
marker - a list of marker indicating future clear regions
public record GroupDebugData(String supervisor, CellType[][] map, Point mapTopLeft, List<InterestingPoint> interestingPoints, PathFindingResult[][] pathFindingResult, Map<Point,String> agentPosition, List<Point> roleZones, List<Point> goalZones, List<String> agents, List<Point> marker) extends Record
The Record GroupDebugData defines a data structure to store information about an agent group.
Author:
Heinz Stadler
